gujarati.context:
Here is a 1-2 line summarization of the Gujarati couplet:

Krishna, the merciful, left from there; 
He came to Venkateswara, saw the life-giving vision of Thakorji's darshan.

transliteration.context:
Here is a summary of the Gujarati couplet:

The ocean's waves are countless and infinite, its heat and power unmatched; 
At night, the moon stays steady, while human efforts are limited by time.
